body_html:
Thanks for @prb12 to point out ExecutorState::NodeDone inside executor.cc. I managed to get send/receive timing by commenting out related code inside executor.cc and compile TensorFlow from source.

Although it does not output a good UI inside chrome://tracing, I am able to analyze the timing from raw JSON file. :)

a detailed explanation here http://stackoverflow.com/a/42823232/3117069
